Hello! Thank you for reaching out to Harmony Music School's customer service. My name is Donald Gonzalez. May I have your name, please?

Hi, Donald. My name is Marilyn Young.

Thank you, Marilyn. How can I assist you today?

I'm feeling a bit anxious about a shipment I was expecting from your school. It hasn't arrived yet.

I'm sorry to hear that, Marilyn. Let me help you resolve this. Could you please provide me with your order number?

Yes, the order number is two four five eight one.

Thank you. Also, can I have your phone number in case we need to contact you further?

Sure, my phone number is five five five three two one zero nine eight seven.

Great, Marilyn. I will check on your shipment status and follow up with you shortly. Is there anything else I can assist you with in the meantime?

No, that's all for now. Thank you, Donald.

You're welcome, Marilyn. Thank you for your patience, and I will get back to you soon. Have a great day!
